io.s4.zeno
Interface JobList

All Known Implementing Classes:
ZKJobList
public interface JobList

A list of Jobs out of which one may be acquired and released, typically at a Site. Example: A list of jobs for ZooKeeper-based clusters.

          Acquire a job, if possible.
